<HEADLINE> Volvo to Take over Whitbread Round-the-world Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, July 9 (Xinhua) -- Swedish vehicle maker AB Volvo
Wednesday said it would take over ownership of the Whitbread Round
the World sailing race from June 1, 1998.
</P>
<P>
