sponsor the 1997-98 event, which begins on September 21 this year
and will be called "The Whitbread Round the World Race for the
Volvo trophy."
</P>
<P>
The race is held once every four years and has been held since
1973.
</P>
<P>
Earlier this year Volvo announced it would no longer sponsor
show jumping events. Volvo is already involved in golf
sponsorship.  
