<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, July 9 (Xinhua) -- Visiting Australian Trade
Minister and Deputy Prime Minister Tim Fischer, Tuesday spoke
highly of South Africa's economic policies which had boosted
foreign investors' confidence, a local daily "The Citizen" reported
today.
</P>
