5,400-sq.m. hot-spring entertainment palace, considered to be the
largest in north China.
</P>
<P>
As the number of tourists increases, developers are setting up
an area with 100 tents nearby as well as hotels, restaurants, and
shopping malls with a combined area of 100,000 sq.m. 
